ownedComment.body: This attribute contains the name of the object to which this selection applies. This may be a(n): - Managed Element: The selection applies to all TPs contained within the Managed Element. - Termination Point (TP): The selection applies only to the named TP. Unlike the case for Managed Element, the operation will not apply to any "contained" TPs. - Management Domain: The selection applies to all TPs contained within the Managed Element. - Subnetwork Connection (SNC): The selection applies to all TPs along the SNC at the same layerRate as the SNC. - Subnetwork: Tthe selection applies to all TPs within all the Managed Elements in the Subnetwork. - Operations System: The selection applies to all TPs within all the Managed Elements associated with the OS.
ownedComment.name: <Unnamed Comment>

publish:property.name: Body
publish:property.publish:value: This attribute contains the name of the object to which this selection applies. This may be a(n):...
